data.description: Welcome Home to this adorable house in High Point.  The quiet front porch is great for drinking coffee, reading a book and would be excellent for a porch swing. Once inside you are met with arched doorways and a brick fireplace with four bedrooms upstairs. The backyard is shaded for endless family cook outs or roasting marshmallows by the fire. Close to restaurants, shopping, gas stations and so much more. You don't want to miss this diamond in the rough! This home qualifies for a home ownership plus program. Contact us for more information.
